      "item_id": "85b425820a:0",
      "text": "点击 toolbar 左侧的 tractor 图标会显示 About Tractor pane。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:1",
      "text": "Engine Version",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:2",
      "text": "显示 Tractor version、build date、build ID 和 platform。与 Tractor Support 沟通以确认正在使用的具体软件版本时，这会很有用。",
      "ascii_letters": 52,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:3",
      "text": "Dashboard Version",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:4",
      "text": "显示 Dashboard 的 Tractor version、build date 和 build ID；对于 custom installation，这些值可能不同于 Engine 的值。",
      "ascii_letters": 63,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:5",
      "text": "Scheduler Mode",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:7",
      "text": "Thread Counts",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "85b425820a:8",
      "text": "显示专用于各种角色的 engine process thread 的数量和类型，例如处理传入 blade request、主动联系 blade（例如终止 active task），以及服务 Dashboard 和其他 client request。",
      "ascii_letters": 68,
